{
  "stem": "18186.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But during the time when we were traveling, I don't remember-- and we were going also-- I don't know how we come-- we went through Berlin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whose husband?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the German-- the Polish family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were going, by the time-- I don't know how this can be-- back to the farm-- we went to the Scheidemuhl.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know we went through the Berlin, and we saw Berlin on fire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw-- we went through the woods, wooded area, we also-- I think it was Berlin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was also a lot, a lot of, killed there from the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We was almost walking on the bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the German Army and the Russian Army, both, because they were fighting for every-- every step.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it took a long-- took a while until-- until we were liberated, until we got to get liberated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then after, when we were liberated, we went back to the-- to the farm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then finally, after a while, they were all Russian, occupied Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the minute we were liberated, we were still in-- we also were hiding in the forest because of these airplanes that, you know, are shooting and things like that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, oh my god.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm liberated?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what about my family?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was because the Russian soldiers came in, and they came to start to speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, the war is over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we came out from the-- forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, oh my god, oh myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What about my family?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did they survive or they didn't?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And where will I find Jewish people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, here where I am now, there's no Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
